      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ASHY BEAR (1) had the drop on the lead and went on to be beaten 1.75 lengths into second (28.97) at this track in a Grade 5/6 over 498m. Didn't win last time but still ran one of the quickest times on the card. Likely to feature again. ANNA RUMBLE (2) was never in contention last time after losing her position early at this track, but prior to that won comfortably by 6 lengths at this track (21.91) beating Blue Marine in a Mix 5 on March 27. Cannot be taken lightly. DIFFERENT HERE (3) latest effort finished 4th over 380m at this track beaten 10 lengths (22.24) behind Lenard Clyde in a Grade 5 on April 2. Looks one of the chances. LOVELY MADELINE (4) must be included on latest effort.",
